      <title>南非煤炭铁路形势恶化，但 Thungela 预计 2025 年将出现转机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/south-africa-coal-rail-worsens-but-thungela-sees-2025-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非铁路煤炭运输量去年跌至30年来最低水平，今年上半年也出现下降，但矿业公司 Thungela Resources Ltd. 预计 2025 年将出现好转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/south-africa-coal-rail-worsens-but-thungela-sees-2025-turnaround</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:56:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>煤炭价格下跌和铁路瓶颈导致 Thungela 利润下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/thungela-profit-slumps-on-lower-coal-prices-and-rail-bottlenecks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非煤炭出口商 Thungela Resources Ltd. 表示，由于价格下跌和铁路中断，上半年利润暴跌近 60%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/thungela-profit-slumps-on-lower-coal-prices-and-rail-bottlenecks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐科威新任部长承诺提高石油产量和投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/jokowi-s-new-ministers-pledge-higher-oil-output-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统佐科·维多多的新部长计划制定政策，以提高石油和天然气产量，并在现任政府执政的最后两个月之外吸引更多的私营部门投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/jokowi-s-new-ministers-pledge-higher-oil-output-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>管道恢复运营后尼日尔恢复通过贝宁出口石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/niger-resumes-oil-exports-through-benin-after-pipeline-reopened</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府官员表示，尼日尔在最近的边境争端之后与邻国贝宁达成协议，并恢复石油出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/niger-resumes-oil-exports-through-benin-after-pipeline-reopened</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:41:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
