    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及延长央行行长任期以显示连续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/egypt-extends-central-banker-s-rule-in-sign-of-policy-continuity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及将哈桑·阿卜杜拉的央行行长任期延长一年，此举或将使投资者放心，这个北非国家在今年早些时候大幅加息和货币贬值后，仍致力于推行正统的货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/egypt-extends-central-banker-s-rule-in-sign-of-policy-continuity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国计划控制乌克兰支出，国防股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/defense-shares-fall-as-germany-plans-to-rein-in-ukraine-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，为控制开支，德国将不再批准乌克兰新的援助请求，欧洲国防类股周一下跌，回吐了今年迄今的部分涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/defense-shares-fall-as-germany-plans-to-rein-in-ukraine-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:34:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
